As a visitor, I can log in or sign up and login

As a user, I can see all nutritionists (nutritionists#index)
As a user, I can see a nutritionist's profile (nutritionists#show)
As a user, I can subscribe to a nutritionist (subscriptions#new and subscriptions#create)

As a user, I can see all recommended meals (meals#index)
As a user, I can see a recommended meal's details (meals#show)

As a user, I can build a meal plan (meal_plans#new and meal_plans#create)
As a user, I can view my daily meal plans (meal_plans#index)
As a user, I can view a daily meal plan (meal_plans#show)











As a user, I can add a review to a nutritionist's profile (review#new and review#create)
As a user, I can edit a review (review#edit and review#update)
As a user, I can delete a review (review#destroy)



Celine' tasks of the day:

As a user, I can see a nutritionist's profile (nutritionists#show)
As a user, I can subscribe to a nutritionist (subscriptions#new and subscriptions#create)
